<text><body>
<lb n="1422b11"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="1422b12"/>
<lb n="1422b13"/><head type="no">No. 2897</head>
<lb n="1422b14"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead><note n="1422001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】大日本續藏經，校者曰原本以鮮本校異，【甲】大英博物館藏燉煌本, S. 127, 甲本首缺</note>佛說天地八陽神&CB00057;經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="1422b15"/>
<lb n="1422b16"/><byline type="Translator">唐三藏法師義淨奉詔譯</byline>
<lb n="1422b17"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛在毘耶達摩城。寥廓宅中。十
<lb n="1422b18"/>方相隨。四眾圍繞。爾時無礙菩薩。在大眾中。
<lb n="1422b19"/>即從座<note n="1422002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">起＋（合掌向佛）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422002"><lem>起</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">起合掌向佛</rdg></app>。而白佛言。世尊。此閻浮提眾生。
<lb n="1422b20"/>遞代相生。無始已來。相續不斷。有識者少。無
<lb n="1422b21"/><note n="1422003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">識＝智&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422003"><lem>識</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">智</rdg></app>者多。念佛者少。<note n="1422004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不念佛者多神通者少不神＝求&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422004"><lem>不念佛者多。神通者少。
<lb n="1422b22"/>不神</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">求</rdg></app>通者多。持戒者少。破戒者多。精進者少。
<lb n="1422b23"/>懈怠者多。智慧者少。愚癡者多。長壽者少。短
<lb n="1422b24"/>命者多。禪定者少。散亂者多。富貴者少。貧賤
<lb n="1422b25"/>者多。柔軟者少。剛強者<note n="1422005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＋（興盛者少惸獨者多正直者少曲諂者多清慎者少貪獨者多）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422005"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">多興盛者少惸獨者多正直者少曲諂者多清慎者少貪獨者多</rdg></app>。布施者少。慳<note n="1422006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貪＝&CB00385;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422006"><lem>貪</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&CB00385;</rdg></app>
<lb n="1422b26"/>者多。信實者少。虛妄者多。被使世俗淺薄。官
<lb n="1422b27"/>法荼毒。賊役煩重。百姓窮苦。<note n="1422007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">取＝所&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="1422007" corr="所" resp="【原】">取</sic>求難得。良
<lb n="1422b28"/>由信邪倒見。獲如是苦。唯願世尊。為諸邪
<lb n="1422b29"/>見眾生。說其正見之法。令得悟解。免於眾
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1422c" n="1422c"/>
<lb n="1422c01"/>苦</p>
<lb n="1422c02"/><p>佛言。善哉善哉。無礙菩薩。汝大慈悲。為諸邪
<lb n="1422c03"/>見眾生。問於如來正見之法。不可思議。汝等
<lb n="1422c04"/>諦聽。善思念之。吾當為汝。分別<note n="1422008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">演＝解&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422008"><lem>演</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">解</rdg></app>說天地
<lb n="1422c05"/>八陽之經。此經過去諸佛已說。未來諸佛當
<lb n="1422c06"/>說。現在諸佛今說。夫天地之間。為人最勝最
<lb n="1422c07"/>上者。貴於一切萬物。人者。真也正也。心無虛
<lb n="1422c08"/>妄。身行正真。左&CB06983;為<note n="1422009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">真＝正&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422009"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">正</rdg></app>。右&CB06983;為<note n="1422010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝真&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422010"><lem>正</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">真</rdg></app>。常行正
<lb n="1422c09"/>真。故名為人。是知人能弘道。以潤身。依道依
<lb n="1422c10"/>人。皆成聖道</p>
<lb n="1422c11"/><p>復次無礙菩薩一切眾生。既得人身。不能修
<lb n="1422c12"/>福。背真向偽。造種種惡業。命將欲終。<note n="1422011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">必沈＝沈淪&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422011"><lem>必沈</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">沈淪</rdg></app>
<lb n="1422c13"/>苦海。受種種罪。若聞此經。信<note n="1422012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝心&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422012"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">心</rdg></app>不逆。即得
<lb n="1422c14"/>解脫諸罪之難。出於苦海。善神加護。無諸障
<lb n="1422c15"/>礙。延年益壽。而無橫夭。以信力故。獲如是
<lb n="1422c16"/>福。何況有人。盡能書寫。受持讀誦。如法修
<lb n="1422c17"/>行。<note n="1422013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔說〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422013"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>其功德。不可稱。不可量。無有邊際。
<lb n="1422c18"/><note n="1422014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">壽＝命&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422014"><lem>壽</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">命</rdg></app>終之後。並得成佛。佛告無礙菩薩摩訶
<lb n="1422c19"/>薩。若有眾生。信邪倒見。即被邪魔外道。魑魅
<lb n="1422c20"/>魍魎。鳥鳴百怪。諸惡鬼神。競來惱亂。與其橫
<lb n="1422c21"/>病。<note n="1422015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（惡種…痛））八字＝（（惡腫惡疰惡忤受其痛苦））&M062403;十字【原】</note><app n="1422015" word-count="8"><lem>惡種惡注。受其苦痛</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">惡腫惡疰惡忤受其痛苦</rdg></app>。無有休息。遇善知
<lb n="1422c22"/>識為讀此經三遍。是諸惡鬼。皆悉消滅。病
<lb n="1422c23"/><note n="1422016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝則&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="1422016"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">則</rdg></app>除愈。身強力足。讀經功德。獲如是福。若
<lb n="1422c24"/>有眾生。多於婬欲瞋恚愚癡慳貪嫉&CB00107;。若見
<lb n="1422c25"/>此經。信敬供養。<anchor id="fxT85p1422c01"/>即讀三遍。愚癡<note n="1422017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等惡＝惡等&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422017"><lem>等惡</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">惡等</rdg></app>。並皆
<lb n="1422c26"/>除滅。慈悲喜捨。得佛法分</p>
<lb n="1422c27"/><p>復次無礙菩薩。若善男子善女人等。興有為
<lb n="1422c28"/>法。先讀此經三遍。築牆動土。安立家宅。南堂
<lb n="1422c29"/>北堂。東<note n="1422018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">廂＝序&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="1422018"><lem>廂</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">序</rdg></app>西<anchor id="fxT85p1422c02"/>廂。&CB00634;舍<note n="1422019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密＝客&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1422019"><lem>密</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">客</rdg></app>屋。門<note n="1422020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原本冠註曰補入戶字</note>戶井&CB01105;。碓
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1423a" n="1423a"/>
<lb n="1423a01"/>磑庫藏。六畜欄圂。日遊月殺。<note n="1423001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423001"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>將軍太歲。
<lb n="1423a02"/>黃幡豹尾。五土地神。青龍白虎。朱雀玄武。六
<lb n="1423a03"/>甲禁諱。十二諸神。土<note n="1423002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">府＝尉&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423002"><lem>府</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">尉</rdg></app>伏龍。一切鬼魅。皆
<lb n="1423a04"/>悉隱藏。遠<note n="1423003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">屏四＝迸他&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423003"><lem>屏四</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">迸他</rdg></app>方。影銷影滅。不敢為害。甚
<lb n="1423a05"/>大吉利。得德無量。善男子。興功之後。堂舍
<lb n="1423a06"/>永安。屋宅牢固。富貴吉昌。不求自得。若遠行
<lb n="1423a07"/>從軍。仕官興生。甚得宜利。門興人貴。百子千
<lb n="1423a08"/>孫。父慈子孝。男忠女貞。兄恭弟順　夫妻
<lb n="1423a09"/>和睦。信義篤親。所願成就。若有眾生。忽被縣
<lb n="1423a10"/>官拘<note n="1423004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">執＝繫&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423004"><lem>執</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">繫</rdg></app>。盜賊牽挽。暫讀此經三遍。即得解
<lb n="1423a11"/>脫。若有善男子善女人。受持讀誦。為<note n="1423005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（人）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423005"><lem>他</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">他人</rdg></app>書
<lb n="1423a12"/>寫<note n="1423006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（天地）&M062403;＋八【原】＊</note><app n="1423006"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">天地八</rdg></app>陽經者。設入水火。不被焚漂。或在
<lb n="1423a13"/>山澤虎<note n="1423007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（狼猛…敢））七字＝（（狼屏&CB00528;不敢搏噬））&M062403;七字【原】</note><app n="1423007" word-count="7"><lem>狼。猛獸屏跡不敢</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">狼屏&CB00528;不敢搏噬</rdg></app>。善神衛護。成無
<lb n="1423a14"/>上道</p>
<lb n="1423a15"/><p>若復有人。多於語綺語惡口兩舌。若能受持
<lb n="1423a16"/>讀誦此經。永除四<note n="1423008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔惡〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423008"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>過。得四無礙辯。而成
<lb n="1423a17"/>佛道</p>
<lb n="1423a18"/><p>若善男子善女人等。父母有罪。臨終之日。當
<lb n="1423a19"/>墮地獄。受無量苦。其子即為<note n="1423009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">讀＋（誦）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423009"><lem>讀</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">讀誦</rdg></app>此經七遍。
<lb n="1423a20"/>父母即離地獄而生天上。見佛聞法。悟無生
<lb n="1423a21"/>忍。以成佛道</p>
<lb n="1423a22"/><p>佛告無礙菩薩。毘婆尸佛時。有優婆塞優婆
<lb n="1423a23"/>夷。心不信邪。<note n="1423010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敬崇＝崇敬&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423010"><lem>敬崇</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">崇敬</rdg></app>佛法。書寫此經。受持讀
<lb n="1423a24"/>誦。<note n="1423011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔所作所為〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423011"><lem>所作所為</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>。須作即作。一無所問。以正信
<lb n="1423a25"/>故。兼行布施。平等供養。得無漏身。成菩提
<lb n="1423a26"/>道。號曰普光如來應正等覺。劫名大<note n="1423012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漏＝滿&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="1423012" corr="滿" resp="【原】">漏</sic>。國
<lb n="1423a27"/>名無邊。但是人民。行菩薩道。無所得法。<note n="1423013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以是…報〕&M062403;九字－【原】</note><app n="1423013" word-count="9"><lem>以
<lb n="1423a28"/>是經威德。獲如是報</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1423a29"/><p>復次無礙菩薩。此<anchor id="fxT85p1423a01"/>八陽經。行<note n="1423014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔在〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423014"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>閻浮提。在
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1423b" n="1423b"/>
<lb n="1423b01"/>在處處。有八菩薩。諸梵天王。一切明靈圍繞
<lb n="1423b02"/>此經。香華供養。如佛無異</p>
<lb n="1423b03"/><p>佛告無礙菩薩摩訶薩<note n="1423015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423015"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>。若善男子善女人
<lb n="1423b04"/>等。為諸眾生。講說此經。深達實相。得甚深
<lb n="1423b05"/>理。即知身心佛身法心。所以能知<anchor id="fxT85p1423b02"/>即<note n="1423016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423016"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>智
<lb n="1423b06"/>慧眼常見種種無盡色。色即是空。空即是色。
<lb n="1423b07"/>受想行識亦空。即是妙色身如來。耳常聞種
<lb n="1423b08"/>種無盡聲。聲即是空。空即是聲。即是妙音聲
<lb n="1423b09"/>如來。鼻常嗅種種無盡香。香即是空。空即是
<lb n="1423b10"/>香。即是香積如來。舌常了種種無盡味。味即
<lb n="1423b11"/>是空。空即是味。即是法喜如來。身常覺種種
<lb n="1423b12"/>無盡觸。觸即是空。空即是觸。即是智明如來。
<lb n="1423b13"/>意常思想能分別種種無盡法。法即是空。空
<lb n="1423b14"/>即是法。即是法明如來</p>
<lb n="1423b15"/><p>善男子。<note n="1423017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔觀〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423017"><lem>觀</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>此六根顯現人皆<note n="1423018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔空〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423018"><lem>空</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>口常說<note n="1423019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之若說＝其&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423019"><lem>之。
<lb n="1423b16"/>若說</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">其</rdg></app>善語。善法常轉。即成聖道。<note n="1423020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423020"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>說邪
<lb n="1423b17"/>語。惡法常轉。即墮地獄。善男子。善惡之理。
<lb n="1423b18"/>不得不信。善男子。人之身心。是佛法器。亦
<lb n="1423b19"/>是十二部大經卷也。無始已來。轉讀不盡。不
<lb n="1423b20"/>損毫毛。如來藏經。唯識心見性者之所能知。
<lb n="1423b21"/>非諸聲聞凡夫所能知。善男子。讀誦此經。深
<lb n="1423b22"/>解真理。即知身心是佛法器。若醉迷不醒。不
<lb n="1423b23"/>了自心。是佛法根本。流<note n="1423021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">轉＝浪&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423021"><lem>轉</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">浪</rdg></app>諸趣。墮於惡道。
<lb n="1423b24"/>永沈苦海。不聞佛法名字</p>
<lb n="1423b25"/><p>爾時五百天子。在大眾中。聞佛所說。得法眼
<lb n="1423b26"/>淨。皆大歡喜。即發無等等阿耨多羅三藐三
<lb n="1423b27"/>菩提心</p>
<lb n="1423b28"/><p>無礙菩薩復白佛言。世尊。人之在世。生死為
<lb n="1423b29"/>重。生不擇日。時至即生。死不擇日。時至即
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1423c" n="1423c"/>
<lb n="1423c01"/>死。何因殯葬即問良辰吉日。然始殯葬。殯葬
<lb n="1423c02"/>之後。還有妨害。貧窮者多。滅門者不少。唯願
<lb n="1423c03"/>世尊。為諸邪見無智眾生。說其因緣。令得正
<lb n="1423c04"/>道。除其顛倒</p>
<lb n="1423c05"/><p>佛言。善哉善哉。善男子。汝實甚能。問於眾生
<lb n="1423c06"/>生死之事。殯葬之法。汝等諦聽。<note n="1423022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔吾〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423022"><lem>吾</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>當為汝
<lb n="1423c07"/>說智慧之理。大道之法。夫天地廣大清。日月
<lb n="1423c08"/>廣長明。時年善美。實無有異。善男子。人王菩
<lb n="1423c09"/>薩。甚大慈悲。愍念眾生。皆如赤子。下為人
<lb n="1423c10"/>主。作<note n="1423023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔蓬〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423023"><lem>蓬</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>民父母。順於俗人。教<note n="1423024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝民&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423024"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">民</rdg></app>俗法。<note n="1423025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">造＝遺&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423025"><lem>造</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">遺</rdg></app>
<lb n="1423c11"/>作曆日。<note n="1423026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">須＝班&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423026"><lem>須</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">班</rdg></app>下天下。令知時節。為有<note n="1423027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平滿＝滿平&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423027"><lem>平滿</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">滿平</rdg></app>。成
<lb n="1423c12"/>收開<note n="1423028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（閉建…危））七字＝（（除之字執危破殺））&M062403;七字【原】</note><app n="1423028" word-count="7"><lem>閉。建除定執。破危</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">除之字執危破殺</rdg></app>之文。愚人依字信
<lb n="1423c13"/>用。無不免其凶禍。又使邪師厭鎮。說是道非。
<lb n="1423c14"/>謾求邪神拜餓鬼。&CB00230;福招殃自受苦。如斯人
<lb n="1423c15"/>皆返天時逆地理。背日月之光明。<note n="1423029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（常）&M062403;＋沒【原】</note><app n="1423029"><lem>沒</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">常沒</rdg></app>闇室。
<lb n="1423c16"/>違正道之廣路。&M010527;尋邪徑。顛倒之甚也。善
<lb n="1423c17"/>男子。產<note n="1423030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔生〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423030"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>時<note n="1423031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">讀＋（誦）&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="1423031"><lem>讀</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">讀誦</rdg></app>此經三遍。兒即易生。甚大
<lb n="1423c18"/>吉利。聰明<note n="1423032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝利&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423032"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">利</rdg></app>慧。福德具足。而不中夭。死時
<lb n="1423c19"/><anchor id="fxT85p1423c03"/>讀此經三遍。一無妨害。得福無量。善男子。
<lb n="1423c20"/>日日<note n="1423033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕&M062403;－【原】＊</note><app n="1423033"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>好日。月月<anchor id="fxT85p1423c04"/>大好月。年年<anchor id="fxT85p1423c05"/>大好年。
<lb n="1423c21"/>實無間隔。但辨即須殯葬。殯葬之日。<anchor id="fxT85p1423c06"/>讀此
<lb n="1423c22"/>經七遍。甚大吉利。獲福無量。門榮人貴。延
<lb n="1423c23"/>年益壽。命終之日。並得成聖<note n="1423034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔道〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1423034"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>。善男子。殯
<lb n="1423c24"/>葬之地。莫問東西南北。安穩之處。諸人愛樂。
<lb n="1423c25"/>鬼神愛樂。即讀此經三遍。便以修<note n="1423035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">榮＝營&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423035"><lem>榮</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">營</rdg></app>。安置
<lb n="1423c26"/>墓<note n="1423036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">內＝田&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423036"><lem>內</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">田</rdg></app>。永無災障。家富人興。甚大吉利。爾時
<lb n="1423c27"/>世尊。欲重宣此義。而說偈言</p>
<lb n="1423c28"/><lg><l>營生善善日</l><l>休殯好好時</l>
<lb n="1423c29"/><l>生死讀誦經</l><l>甚得大<note n="1423037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利益＝吉利&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1423037"><lem>利益</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">吉利</rdg></app></l>
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1424a" n="1424a"/>
<lb n="1424a01"/><l>月月善明月</l><l>年年大好年</l>
<lb n="1424a02"/><l>讀經即殯葬</l><l>榮花萬代<note n="1424001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以上甲本缺</note>昌</l></lg>
<lb n="1424a03"/><p>爾時眾中。七萬七千人。聞佛所說。心開意
<lb n="1424a04"/>解。捨邪歸正得佛法分。永斷疑惑。皆<note n="1424002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">發＝得【甲】</note><app n="1424002"><lem>發</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>阿
<lb n="1424a05"/>耨多羅三<corr sic="貌">藐</corr>三菩提<note n="1424003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424003"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1424a06"/><p>無礙菩薩。復白佛言。世尊。一切凡夫。皆以婚
<lb n="1424a07"/>媾為親。先問相宜。<note n="1424004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後＝復【甲】</note><app n="1424004"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>取吉日。然始成親。<note n="1424005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成親之＝已【甲】</note><app n="1424005"><lem>成
<lb n="1424a08"/>親之</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>後。富貴<note n="1424006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">偕＝皆【甲】</note><app n="1424006"><lem>偕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">皆</rdg></app>老者少。貧<note n="1424007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">窮＝寒【甲】</note><app n="1424007"><lem>窮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">寒</rdg></app>生離死別者
<lb n="1424a09"/><note n="1424008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔多〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424008"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。一種信邪。如何而有差別。唯願世尊。為
<lb n="1424a10"/>決眾疑</p>
<lb n="1424a11"/><p>佛言。善男子。汝等諦聽。當為汝說。夫天<note n="1424009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陽＝陰【甲】</note><app n="1424009"><lem>陽</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">陰</rdg></app>
<lb n="1424a12"/>地<note n="1424010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陰＝陽【甲】</note><app n="1424010"><lem>陰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">陽</rdg></app>。月陰日陽。水陰火陽。<note n="1424011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女陰男陽＝男陰女陽【甲】</note><app n="1424011"><lem>女陰男陽</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">男陰女陽</rdg></app>。天地
<lb n="1424a13"/>氣合。一切草木生焉。日月交通。四時八節明
<lb n="1424a14"/>焉。水火相承。一切萬物熟焉。男女允諧。子孫
<lb n="1424a15"/>興焉。皆是天之常道。自然之理。世<note n="1424012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諦＝帝【甲】</note><app n="1424012"><lem>諦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">帝</rdg></app>之法。
<lb n="1424a16"/>善男子。<note n="1424013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔愚〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424013"><lem>愚</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>人無智。信其邪師。卜問望吉。而
<lb n="1424a17"/>不修善。造種種惡業。命終之後。復得人身者。
<lb n="1424a18"/>如指甲上土。墮於地獄。作<note n="1424014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畜餓鬼者＝餓鬼畜生【甲】</note><app n="1424014"><lem>畜餓鬼者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">餓鬼畜生</rdg></app>。如大
<lb n="1424a19"/>地土。善男子。復得人身。正信修善者。如指甲
<lb n="1424a20"/>上土。<note n="1424015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">信邪造惡業者＝不信修善【甲】</note><app n="1424015"><lem>信邪造惡業者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">不信修善</rdg></app>。如大地土。善男子。
<lb n="1424a21"/><note n="1424016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝若【甲】</note><app n="1424016"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>結婚親。莫問水火相剋。<note n="1424017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">胎胞＝胞胎&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424017"><lem>胎胞</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">胞胎</rdg></app>相厭。<note n="1424018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔年紀不同〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424018"><lem>年
<lb n="1424a22"/><note n="1424019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">紀＝命&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424019"><lem>紀</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">命</rdg></app>不同</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。唯看祿命<note n="1424020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">書＋（即）【甲】</note><app n="1424020"><lem>書</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">書即</rdg></app>。知福德多少。以為眷
<lb n="1424a23"/>屬。呼迎之日。<note n="1424021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424021"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>讀此經三遍<note n="1424022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝即【甲】</note><app n="1424022"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>以成禮。此
<lb n="1424a24"/>乃善善相因。明明相屬。門高人貴。子孫興盛。
<lb n="1424a25"/>聰明利<note n="1424023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＋（多才多藝）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424023"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">智多才多藝</rdg></app>。孝敬相承。甚大吉利。而無中夭。
<lb n="1424a26"/>福德具<note n="1424024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">足＋（而生）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424024"><lem>足</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">足而生</rdg></app>。皆成佛道。<note n="1424025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1424025"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>時有八菩薩。承佛
<lb n="1424a27"/>威神。得大總持。常處人間。和光同塵。破邪立
<lb n="1424a28"/><note n="1424026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＋（度四生處八解而不自異）&M062403;【原】，（度四生處八解）【甲】</note><app n="1424026"><lem>正</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">正度四生處八解而不自異</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">正度四生處八解</rdg></app>。其名曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1424b" n="1424b"/>
<lb n="1424b01"/><lg><l>跋陀<note n="1424027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝和【甲】</note><app n="1424027"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">和</rdg></app>菩薩漏盡和</l><l>羅&CB00444;竭菩薩漏盡和</l>
<lb n="1424b02"/><l>憍<note n="1424028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝目【甲】</note><app n="1424028"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">目</rdg></app>兜菩薩漏盡和</l><l><note n="1424029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那羅達菩薩漏盡和∞須彌深菩薩漏盡和【甲】</note><app n="1424029"><lem>那羅達菩薩漏盡和</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">須彌深菩薩漏盡和</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="1424b03"/><l><note n="1424030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那羅達菩薩漏盡和∞須彌深菩薩漏盡和【甲】</note><app n="1424030"><lem>須彌深菩薩漏盡和</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">那羅達菩薩漏盡和</rdg></app></l><l>因<note n="1424031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">桓＝抵&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424031"><lem>桓</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">抵</rdg></app>達菩薩漏盡和</l>
<lb n="1424b04"/><l>和輪調菩薩漏盡和</l><l>無緣觀菩薩漏盡和</l></lg>
<lb n="1424b05"/><p>是八菩薩。俱白佛言。世尊。我等於諸佛所。
<lb n="1424b06"/>受<note n="1424032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔持〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424032"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得陀羅尼神&CB00057;。而今說之。擁護受持
<lb n="1424b07"/><note n="1424033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔讀誦〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424033"><lem>讀誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT85p1424b01"/>八陽經者。永無恐怖。使一切不善之
<lb n="1424b08"/>物。不得侵損讀經法師。即於佛前而說&CB00057;
<lb n="1424b09"/>曰</p>
<lb n="1424b10"/><p rend="margin-left:1" type="dharani">阿佉尼<note n="1424034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424034"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>尼佉尼<note n="1424035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424035"><lem><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿<note n="1424036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毘＝比【甲】</note><app n="1424036"><lem>毘</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">比</rdg></app>羅<note n="1424037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424037"><lem><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曼隸<note n="1424038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424038"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="1424b11"/>曼多隸<note n="1424039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五娑婆訶〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424039"><lem><note place="inline">五</note>娑婆訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1424b12"/><p>世尊。若有不善者。欲來惱法師。聞我說此&CB00057;。
<lb n="1424b13"/>頭破作七分。如阿梨樹枝</p>
<lb n="1424b14"/><p><note n="1424040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾＝是【甲】</note><app n="1424040"><lem>爾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>時無邊身菩薩。<note n="1424041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即從座起前〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424041"><lem>即從座起。前</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>白佛言。世
<lb n="1424b15"/>尊。云何名為<anchor id="fxT85p1424b02"/>八陽經。唯願世尊。為諸聽眾。
<lb n="1424b16"/>解說其義。令得<note n="1424042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">覺＝醒【甲】</note><app n="1424042"><lem>覺</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">醒</rdg></app>悟。速達<note n="1424043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">本心＝心本【甲】</note><app n="1424043"><lem>本心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">心本</rdg></app>。入佛知見。
<lb n="1424b17"/>永斷疑悔</p>
<lb n="1424b18"/><p>佛言。善哉善哉。善男子。汝等諦聽。吾今為
<lb n="1424b19"/><note n="1424044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汝＋（分別）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424044"><lem>汝</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">汝分別</rdg></app>解說<anchor id="fxT85p1424b03"/>八陽之經<note n="1424045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝天者陰也地者陽也&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424045"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">天者陰也地者陽也</rdg></app>。八者分別也。陽者明
<lb n="1424b20"/>解也。明解大乘<note n="1424046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空無＝無為【甲】</note><app n="1424046"><lem>空無</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">無為</rdg></app>之理。了能分別。<note n="1424047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424047"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>識
<lb n="1424b21"/>因緣。<note n="1424048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空＋（實）【甲】</note><app n="1424048"><lem>空</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">空實</rdg></app>無所得。<note n="1424049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">云何＝又云&M062403;【原】，〔云何〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424049"><lem>云何</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">又云</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>八識<note n="1424050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔名〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424050"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>為經。<note n="1424051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八陽名＝陽明【甲】</note><app n="1424051"><lem>八陽
<lb n="1424b22"/>名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">陽明</rdg></app>為緯。經緯相<note n="1424052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">交＝投&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424052"><lem>交</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">投</rdg></app>。以<note n="1424053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成＝為【甲】</note><app n="1424053"><lem>成</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>經教。故<note n="1424054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＋（為）【甲】</note><app n="1424054"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">名為</rdg></app>八陽
<lb n="1424b23"/>經。<note n="1424055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＋（識）【甲】</note><app n="1424055"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">八識</rdg></app><note n="1424056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＋（是）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1424056"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">者是</rdg></app><note n="1424057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八識…識〕七字－【甲】</note><note n="1424057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔八識〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424057"><lem>八識</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="1424058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔云何…識〕&M062403;三十一字－【原】</note><note n="1424058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔云何名八識眼是色識耳是聲識鼻是香識。舌者是味識身是觸識意是分別識〕&M062403;三十一字－【原】，〔云何名八識〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424058"><lem>云何名八識。眼是色識耳
<lb n="1424b24"/>是聲識。鼻是香識。舌<note n="1424059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424059"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>是味識。身是觸識。
<lb n="1424b25"/>意是分別識</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">眼是色識耳是聲識鼻是香識。舌者是味識身是觸識意是分別識</rdg></app>。<note n="1424060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔六根是六識〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424060"><lem>六根是六識</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。含藏<note n="1424061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">識＋（是）【甲】</note><app n="1424061"><lem>識</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">識是</rdg></app>。阿賴耶
<lb n="1424b26"/>識。是名<note n="1424062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424062"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>八識。明了分<note n="1424063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">別＝明【甲】</note><app n="1424063"><lem>別</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">明</rdg></app>八識<note n="1424064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">根源＝相漁【甲】</note><app n="1424064"><lem>根源</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">相漁</rdg></app>。空
<lb n="1424b27"/>無所<note n="1424065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝有【甲】</note><app n="1424065"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">有</rdg></app>。即知兩眼<note n="1424066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="1424066"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>光明天。<note n="1424067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔光明天〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424067"><lem>光明天</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>中。
<lb n="1424b28"/>即現日月光明。世尊。兩耳<anchor id="fxT85p1424b04"/>是聲<note n="1424068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聞〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424068"><lem>聞</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>天。聲聞
<lb n="1424b29"/>天中。即現無量<note n="1424069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聲〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424069"><lem>聲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>如來。兩鼻<anchor id="fxT85p1424b05"/>是佛香天。
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1424c" n="1424c"/>
<lb n="1424c01"/>佛香天中。即現香積如來。<note n="1424070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">口＋（舌）【甲】</note><app n="1424070"><lem>口</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">口舌</rdg></app>是法味天。法
<lb n="1424c02"/>味天中。即現法<note n="1424071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜＝慧【甲】</note><app n="1424071"><lem>喜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">慧</rdg></app>如來。身是盧舍那天。<note n="1424072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔盧舍那天〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424072"><lem>盧
<lb n="1424c03"/>舍那天</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>中。即現<note n="1424073" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔成就〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424073"><lem>成就</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>盧舍那佛。盧舍那鏡
<lb n="1424c04"/>像佛。盧舍那光明佛。意是無分別天。無分別
<lb n="1424c05"/>天中。即現不動如來。大光明佛。心是法界天。
<lb n="1424c06"/><note n="1424074" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔法界天〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424074"><lem>法界天</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>中。即現空王如來。含藏識天。演
<lb n="1424c07"/>出阿那含經。大<note n="1424075" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔般〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424075"><lem>般</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>涅槃經。阿賴耶識天。演
<lb n="1424c08"/>出大智度論經。瑜伽論經。善男子。佛即是
<lb n="1424c09"/>法。法即是佛。合為一相。即現大通智勝如
<lb n="1424c10"/>來</p>
<lb n="1424c11"/><p>佛說此經時。一切大地。六種震動。光照天
<lb n="1424c12"/><note n="1424076" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔地〕－【甲】</note><app n="1424076"><lem>地</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。無有邊際。浩浩蕩蕩。而無所名。一切幽
<lb n="1424c13"/>冥。<note n="1424077" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉皆＝皆悉【甲】</note><app n="1424077"><lem>悉皆</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">皆悉</rdg></app>明朗。一切地獄。&CB00278;皆消滅。一切罪
<lb n="1424c14"/>人。俱得離苦。<note n="1424078" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔皆發…心〕&M062403;七字－【原】</note><app n="1424078" word-count="7"><lem>皆<note n="1424079" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">發＝登【甲】</note><app n="1424079"><lem>發</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">登</rdg></app>無上菩提心</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1424c15"/><p>爾時<note n="1424080" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大眾之＝眾【甲】</note><app n="1424080"><lem>大眾之</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">眾</rdg></app>中。八萬八千菩薩。一時成佛。
<lb n="1424c16"/>號曰<note n="1424081" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空王＝虛空藏【甲】</note><app n="1424081"><lem>空王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">虛空藏</rdg></app>如來應正等覺。劫名<note n="1424082" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">離苦＝圓滿【甲】</note><app n="1424082"><lem>離苦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">圓滿</rdg></app>。國號
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1425a" n="1425a"/>
<lb n="1425a01"/>無邊。一切<note n="1425001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（人民…萬））十七字＝（（民人無有彼此並諍三昧））十字【甲】</note><app n="1425001" word-count="17"><lem>人民。皆行菩薩六波羅<note n="1425002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＋（無有彼此證無諍三昧）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1425002"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">蜜無有彼此證無諍三昧</rdg></app>。逮無
<lb n="1425a02"/>所得<note n="1425003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔法〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1425003"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>。六萬</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">民人無有彼此並諍三昧</rdg></app>六千比丘。比丘尼。優婆塞。優
<lb n="1425a03"/>婆夷。得大總持。<note n="1425004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔入不二法門〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425004"><lem>入不二法門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。無數天龍夜
<lb n="1425a04"/>叉。乾闥婆。阿<note n="1425005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">修＝脩【甲】</note><app n="1425005"><lem>修</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">脩</rdg></app>羅。迦樓羅。緊那羅。摩&CB00264;羅
<lb n="1425a05"/>伽。人非人等。得法眼淨。行菩薩道</p>
<lb n="1425a06"/><p><note n="1425006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復次〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="1425006"><lem>復次</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>善男子。<note n="1425007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若復〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425007"><lem>若復</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>有人。得官登<note n="1425008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">位＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="1425008"><lem>位</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">位之</rdg></app>日。及
<lb n="1425a07"/><note n="1425009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入新＝新入【甲】</note><app n="1425009"><lem>入新</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">新入</rdg></app>宅之<note n="1425010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時暫＝日即【甲】</note><app n="1425010"><lem>時。暫</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">日即</rdg></app>讀此經三遍。甚大吉利。
<lb n="1425a08"/><note n="1425011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（善神…足））十二字＝（（獲福無量））四字【甲】</note><app n="1425011" word-count="12"><lem>善神加護。延年益壽。福德具足</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">獲福無量</rdg></app>。善男子。若
<lb n="1425a09"/>讀此經一遍。如讀一切經一<note n="1425012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">部＝遍【甲】</note><app n="1425012"><lem>部</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">遍</rdg></app>。<note n="1425013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若書＝能【甲】</note><app n="1425013"><lem>若書</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">能</rdg></app>寫一
<lb n="1425a10"/><note n="1425014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">卷＋（者）【甲】</note><app n="1425014"><lem>卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">卷者</rdg></app>。如<note n="1425015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔書〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425015"><lem>書</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>寫一切經一部。其功德不可稱。不
<lb n="1425a11"/>可量。<note n="1425016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔等空〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425016"><lem>等<note n="1425017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（虛）&M062403;＋空【原】</note><app n="1425017"><lem>空</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">虛空</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無有邊<note n="1425018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔際〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425018"><lem>際</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="1425019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（如斯…道））九字＝（（成聖道果））&M062403;四字【原】</note><app n="1425019" word-count="9"><lem>如斯人等。即成
<lb n="1425a12"/><note n="1425020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔就〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425020"><lem>就</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>聖道</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">成聖道果</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1425a13"/><p>復次無邊身菩薩摩訶薩。若有眾生。不信正
<lb n="1425a14"/>法。常生邪見。忽聞此經。即生誹謗言非佛說。
<lb n="1425a15"/>是人現世。得白<note n="1425021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">癩＝賴【甲】</note><app n="1425021"><lem>癩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賴</rdg></app>病。惡瘡膿血。遍體交流。
<lb n="1425a16"/>腥<note n="1425022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臊＝&CB05369;【甲】</note><app n="1425022"><lem>臊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB05369;</rdg></app>臭穢。人皆憎嫉。命<note n="1425023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">終＝經【甲】</note><app n="1425023"><lem>終</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">經</rdg></app>之<note n="1425024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＝後【甲】</note><app n="1425024"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">後</rdg></app>。即墮阿
<lb n="1425a17"/>鼻無間地獄。上火徹下。下火徹上。<note n="1425025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔鐵槍〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425025"><lem>鐵槍</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>鐵
<lb n="1425a18"/>叉。遍體穿<note n="1425026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穴融＝六五藏洋【甲】</note><app n="1425026"><lem>穴。融</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">六五藏洋</rdg></app>銅灌口。<note n="1425027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">筋＝肋【甲】</note><app n="1425027"><lem>筋</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">肋</rdg></app>骨爛壞。一日一
<lb n="1425a19"/>夜。萬死萬生。受大苦痛。無有休息。謗斯經
<lb n="1425a20"/>故。獲罪如是。<note n="1425028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛為…言〕八字－【甲】</note><app n="1425028" word-count="8"><lem>佛為罪人。而說偈言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1425a21"/><lg><l>身是自然身</l><l><note n="1425029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五體自然足〕－【甲】</note><app n="1425029"><lem>五體自然足</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="1425a22"/><l>長乃自然長</l><l>老<note n="1425030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝則&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1425030"><lem>乃</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">則</rdg></app>自然老</l>
<lb n="1425a23"/><l>生<note n="1425031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝則【甲】＊</note><app n="1425031"><lem>乃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">則</rdg></app>自然生</l><l>死<anchor id="fxT85p1425a01"/>乃自然死</l>
<lb n="1425a24"/><l>求長不得長</l><l>求短不得短</l>
<lb n="1425a25"/><l>苦樂汝自當</l><l>邪正由汝已</l>
<lb n="1425a26"/><l>欲作有為功</l><l>讀經莫問師</l>
<lb n="1425a27"/><l>千千萬萬<note n="1425032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝代【甲】</note><app n="1425032"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">代</rdg></app></l><l>得道轉法輪</l></lg>
<lb n="1425a28"/><p>佛說此經已。一切<note n="1425033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝聽【甲】</note><app n="1425033"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">聽</rdg></app>眾。得未曾有。心明意
<lb n="1425a29"/>淨。歡喜踊躍。皆見諸相非相。入佛知見。悟佛
<lb n="1425a30"/>知見。無入無悟。無知無見。不得一法。即涅槃
<pb ed="T" id="T85.2897.1425b" n="1425b"/>
<lb n="1425b01"/>樂<note n="1425034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故此…行〕十七字－【甲】</note><app n="1425034" word-count="17"><lem>故。此諸菩薩聖眾。天神地祇。皆悉歡喜
<lb n="1425b02"/>奉行</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="1425b03"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說天地八陽神&CB00057;經<note n="1425035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">終＝一卷【甲】</note><app n="1425035"><lem>終</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
